                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>\n                                        <placeName>Benton, Ala.</placeName>\n                                        <date>February 3d 1851</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Mr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Sir</p>\n                              <p>We have daly<add>?</add>\n                                        <sic>resived</sic> your letter from last<lb/> year &amp;\n                                        your <add>?</add> &amp; use a all possible<lb/> efforts to\n                                        procure subscriber to your two paper;<lb/> but as the Jews\n                                        here are very indiffer-<lb/>ent we could only get one\n                                                  <sic>suscriber</sic><lb/> to your Jewish Advocate.\n                                        You will send<lb/> also the Occident &amp; the Advocate<lb/>\n                                        to us, <sic>adressed</sic> to <persName>Meyers\n                                                  Richara</persName>.<lb/> The other Jewish Advocate\n                                        you will<lb/> please to send it to <persName>S.\n                                                  Jacobstein</persName>,<lb/>\n                                        <placeName>Benton, Ala.</placeName> &amp; we will do our\n                                        best<lb/> to get some more of them; on that<lb/> account we\n                                                  <add>?</add> send you the<lb/> Prospect back. As\n                                        soon as you<lb/> send the first volumes of <add>?</add>\n                                        papers,<lb/> we will remit you the amount for<lb/> it by\n                                        mail. Please let us so<add>?</add><lb/> hear something about\n                                        the Jews in <placeName>Germany</placeName><lb/> from the\n                                                  <placeName>old Rhine</placeName>. If you excuse us\n                                        we<lb/> would make to you the proposition to use <persName>Dr's<lb/>\n                                                  <add>?</add></persName>\n                                        <add>?</add> &amp; extract occasion<lb/> by some of interest\n                                        or the Orient<add>?</add>\n                                        <add>?</add>.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Hoping this will find you in best health</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">We remain your</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Meyers Rishara</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Mr B Rishara</persName>\n                              </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3zs2m02s/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
